high_descs: Turn around and walk to the green vanity with the white counter on the right.
Pick up the bar of soap in between the yellow spray bottle and another bar of soap on the counter.
Turn around and face right at the wall to reach the sink.
Put the bar of soap inside the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the drawers under the vanity on the left.
Open the bottom drawer under the roll of toilet paper on the vanity, put the rinsed bar of soap inside and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed bar of soap in a drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and take two steps then turn right.
Pick up the bar of soap that's closest to the yellow spray bottle.
Turn around and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the sink.
Get the soap wet in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn right and walk to the drawers leaving enough room to open the drawers to use them.
Open the drawer under the roll of toilet paper and put the soap in the back left corner and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet bar of soap in the drawer.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the bathroom counter to your right.
Grab the soap between the spray bottle and the other soap on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the sink to your right.
Place the soap in the sink, wash it and remove it.
Turn right and walk back to the counter straight ahead.
Place the soap into the counter drawer below.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean piece of soap into the counter drawer.
